[thinking] **Considering serialization issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I need to figure out how to get serialization metadata directly into Native without relying on metadata files, which seems impossible. It looks like I'll need to use a direct generator class to ensure that Native Image includes serializable classes. However, Native Image requires registration for those classes. I'm realizing that if the Object constructor is unregistered, all custom serialization might fail. Can I force the Object constructor metadata using reflection? Hmm, I'm not sure if that’s allowed, though!
